General_Description: '''Pressed for Time''' is a virtual representation of one of [[Kassandra]]'s genetic memories, relived by [[Layla Hassan]] through the portable [[Animus|Animus HR-8.5]].
Section_Riddle: ''If you slip beside the [[Leader House, Phokis|Leader's house]] in [[Pilgrim's Landing]], you can find me in a large bowl of [[olive]]s.''
Section_Outcome: Kassandra found and recovered the engraving.
